    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It suffers from significant mechanical issues, including an engine that runs very roughly and a transmission that slips occasionally. The exterior shows heavy wear with multiple dents, faded paint, and some rust spots, while the interior has several tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car will require a substantial investment in repairs to be roadworthy again.",
